{
  "text": "In summary, this update describes a modified approach to concerns that have arisen from our experiences following the publication in 2015 of our design and analysis guidelines. The areas of focus have been selected from our internal audits as issues requiring reconsideration and aspects of experimentation that we did not consider in the first iteration. Our intention is to continue to support the Pharmacology community in identifying strategies that support and enable transparency and reproducibility. As we stated previously [CITATION_1] , some of our guidance is arbitrary, and some will change. We will make progress, but it will need clear requirements and constant vigilance with progress made in stages. This is our stage II.",
  "citation_candidates": [
    "35449519",
